OL,3,CPolice continue to investigate bishop
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing a boy
OL,6,FPolice are continuing to investigate a
OL,7,Fformer bishop who was jailed earlier
OL,8,Fthis year for sexually abusing a boy.
OL,10,FAnthony Pierce, 84, who was bishop of
OL,11,FSwansea and Brecon between 1999 and
OL,12,F2008, was jailed for four years and
OL,13,Fone month in March for the offences.
OL,15,FHe pleaded guilty to five counts of
OL,16,Findecent assault on a male child under
OL,17,Fthe age of 16, committed while he was
OL,18,Fa parish priest in Swansea in the
OL,19,F1980s.
