OL,6,FIt emerged after Pierce was jailed
OL,7,Fthat a separate allegation of sexual
OL,8,Fabuse against him had been reported to
OL,9,Fsenior figures in the Church in Wales
OL,10,Fin 1993 but was only reported to
OL,11,Fpolice in 2010, by which time the
OL,12,Fvictim had died.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, the BBC reported officers
OL,15,Fwere also investigating an unnamed
OL,16,Fformer vicar over allegations of
OL,17,Fhistoric sexual abuse.
