OL,3,CPolice continue to investigate bishop
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing a boy
OL,6,FIt is the latest controversy to hit
OL,7,Fthe Church in Wales after the
OL,8,FArchbishop of Wales retired in June
OL,9,Ffollowing safeguarding concerns at
OL,10,FBangor Cathedral, which identified "a
OL,11,Fculture in which sexual boundaries
OL,12,Fseemed blurred" and "promiscuity was
OL,13,Facceptable".
OL,15,FThere is no suggestion the archbishop
OL,16,Fbehaved inappropriately.
