OL,3,CPolice continue to investigate bishop
OL,4,Cjailed for sexually abusing a boy
OL,6,FResponding to BBC reporting, Wales'
OL,7,FChildren's Commissioner Rocio
OL,8,FCifuentes said: "We already know that
OL,9,Fthere is a stark lack of independent
OL,10,Foversight of safeguarding arrangements
OL,11,Fin religious institutions in Wales,
OL,12,Fand a need for much stronger external
OL,13,Faccountability in this area. All
OL,14,Foptions should now be under active
OL,15,Fconsideration by Government, including
OL,16,Flegislative change.
