OL,6,FShe added: "I'm also calling for the
OL,7,Freview currently underway of the
OL,8,FNational Independent Safeguarding
OL,9,FBoard's remit to directly address some
OL,10,Fof these questions. This review should
OL,11,Fprovide clarity on how the Independent
OL,12,FInquiry into Child Sexual Abuse's
OL,13,F(IICSA) call for a robust Child
OL,14,FProtection Authority can be met."
OL,16,FIn a statement, the Church in Wales
OL,17,Fsaid the issues which had been raised
OL,18,F` both historic and more recent ` are
OL,19,Fa source of "deepest concern" for the
OL,20,Fchurch.
