OL,6,F"There is no place in the church for
OL,7,Fabuse, misconduct or concealment, and
OL,8,Fwe are determined that the issues
OL,9,Fidentified will be fully addressed,
OL,10,Fand practices improved so that all
OL,11,Fchurch members, and the wider society,
OL,12,Fcan have confidence that the church
OL,13,Fis, as it should be, a safe and
OL,14,Fsupportive environment for all," a
OL,15,Fspokesman said.
OL,17,F"Where we have fallen short of those
OL,18,Fstandards, whether in the past or the
OL,19,Fpresent, we are profoundly sorry and
OL,20,Fapologise to anyone who has suffered
OL,21,For been let down by those failings.
