OL,6,F"It is important to note that the
OL,7,Fissues raised in these questions
OL,8,Frelate to a period of more than 40
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,F"During that time, the process of
OL,12,Fhandling safeguarding concerns within
OL,13,Fthe Church in Wales has undergone
OL,14,Fcontinual review and improvement, so
OL,15,Fthat current procedures are far more
OL,16,Findependent, professional and robust
OL,17,Fthan in previous decades.
